* Iron Raptor keeps her eyes on the new bot, wondering if he was ever going 
to respond. But she doubted it.
She rolls her eyes as she gets Prowls thoughts, not his reply. But the ones 
which he had looked over her body before she had transformed.
Men!  ;)

But the beast in her mind almost seemed to urge her on, wanting her to make 
the first move instead of talking this out.
Though, she simply brushed it aside as easily as an after thought, the beast 
obviously offended but still there.
Her mind snapping out at it: " This is MY mind now and if you don't like it 
you can gladly leave. You won't be missed!"
The creature simply gave her a look as if it were calling her a bitch right 
out, then settled down.
But then the creature turnes on Prowls thoughts as they filter into Iron 
Raptors mind, basically growling at him and asking him how he could put up 
with her.

Iron Raptor simply ignores the creature, turning her attention towards 
Shadow again, the wind picking up and making the cape shift and blow around 
her. Her hair shifting about her head as the sun grew higher in the sky.
Suddenly hearing Klusters transmission in her head, wondering just how many 
times he had broudcasted this until she heard the word three.
THREE! And the Maximals still weren't there yet!?
This was the first time that she had heard this, so at least she had an 
excuse. But the others.
Iron Raptor sighed.
Enough with this Shadow...she had Maximals to rally!

Iron Raptor looked towards Prowl as he contacted her through his mind, still 
finding this all so new. Thinking how all of this had happened so quickly.
Slumping slightly in her armor.*

< Yeah. I heard. Boy! Is everyone in for a few surprises...providing that 
they ever get to base.>

* But then she, somehow, found the command to her new com-link and opened it 
to all the Maximal frequencies. Making her voice very clear and with 
command.*

" All Maximals, this is Iron Raptor. You've all already been given the 
command to return to base. Respond to it. There is no excuse acceptable for 
not doing so unless there is battle or you can give me a better one.
Now, please return to base!"

* Iron Raptor then deactivated the comm and looked at Prowl.*

< Let's get going.>
